<p class="Normal" xmlns:news="http://www.dotnetnuke.com/modules/news" xmlns:newsext="urn:NewsExtensions">Being proficient in a competency means the ability to respond and perform effectively every day, as waves of change wash over us in HR and business. What is the best way to develop that proficiency?<img src="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~r/shrm/hrnews/~4/D8MkPiIQirE" height="1" width="1" alt=""/></p>
